{SOUTH has 17 points and six \Hs. 
This is a mid-range 1\H opening bid.

With 9 points, (1 for the doubleton), NORTH raises to 2\H.

SOUTH's hand is worth one more try. He invites with 3\H.

NORTH had a strong 2\H raise, considering that she might 
have only had 6 points. So she carries on to 4\H.}

